service_read_only_data Struct Reference

#include <service_list.h>


Data Fields

unsigned long pos
uint64_t mod_time

Detailed Description

Data that are only valid after performing get_service_at() and can be outdated by a subsequent call to another function performing a write operation like replace_service_at().

Field Documentation

uint64_t service_read_only_data::mod_time

The last modification time of an already saved service (i.e., this will always be 0 for a new unsaved service).

unsigned long service_read_only_data::pos

The service position in the SSID starting from 0.
